data.enText: to go to a party without a partner
to go to a party without a partner

tr: a male deer, especially an adult male red deer

example: He told on his classmate who had cheated on the exam

tr: attend a dance or a party without a female companion

value.def: A stag is an adult male deer belonging to one of the larger species of deer. Stags usually have large branch-like horns called antlers.

trans: 男子婚前夜(常与男性朋友一同度过)
